snippet.title: GRIP: Combat Racing - Trailer (Nintendo Switch)
snippet.description:
GRIP: Combat Racing comes to Nintendo Switch on November 6th.

Official Website: http://www.nintendo.co.uk/Games/Nintendo-Switch/GRIP-1452442.html

You can pre-order now at the Nintendo Official UK Store: https://store.nintendo.co.uk/nintendo-switch-game/grip-combat-racing-official-soundtrack-cd/11927591.html 

► Subscribe: https://www.youtube.com/user/NintendoUKofficial/?sub_confirmation=1
